casebody.data:
Rubin R. WEEKS, Petitioner
v.
Jason LEWIS, Warden No. 19-5519 Supreme Court of the United States. October 7, 2019

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and the petition *336for a writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eighth Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
